This script grabs the contents of the Yesod Book (http://yesodweb.com/book) and makes PDF file out of it.

Preparations.
Install wkhtmltopdf binaries from http://code.google.com/p/wkhtmltopdf/downloads/list or from source and be sure it uses patched qt library
    cabal install hxt HandsomeSoup
    ulimit -n 10000
    ghc makebook.hs

Run it!
    ./makebook
